			"styles": "\n\t/* Test dimension values with various units */\n\tdiv {\n\t\t/* Length units - absolute */\n\t\twidth: 100px;\n\t\theight: 2cm;\n\t\tmargin: 1mm;\n\t\tpadding: 72pt;\n\t\tborder-width: 6pc;\n\t\ttop: 1in;\n\t\t/* Length units - font-relative */\n\t\tfont-size: 16px;\n\t\tline-height: 1.5em;\n\t\tletter-spacing: 0.1rem;\n\t\tword-spacing: 2ex;\n\t\ttab-size: 4ch;\n\t\t/* Length units - viewport-relative */\n\t\tmax-width: 80vw;\n\t\tmax-height: 90vh;\n\t\tmin-width: 10vmin;\n\t\tmin-height: 10vmax;\n\t\t/* Modern viewport units (small) */\n\t\twidth: 100svw;\n\t\theight: 100svh;\n\t\tmin-width: 10svmin;\n\t\tmax-height: 90svmax;\n\t\t/* Modern viewport units (large) */\n\t\twidth: 100lvw;\n\t\theight: 100lvh;\n\t\t/* Modern viewport units (dynamic) */\n\t\twidth: 100dvw;\n\t\theight: 100dvh;\n\t\t/* Modern viewport units (logical) */\n\t\tinline-size: 50vi;\n\t\tblock-size: 50vb;\n\t\t/* Container query units */\n\t\tpadding: 5cqw 5cqh;\n\t\tmargin: 2cqi 2cqb;\n\t\tgap: 1cqmin;\n\t\tflex-basis: 10cqmax;\n\t\t/* Typography units (Level 4) */\n\t\tfont-size: 2cap;\n\t\twidth: 10ic;\n\t\tline-height: 2lh;\n\t\tmargin-top: 1rlh;\n\t\t/* Percentage */\n\t\topacity: 50%;\n\t\t/* Angle units */\n\t\ttransform: rotate(45deg);\n\t\ttransform: rotate(1rad);\n\t\ttransform: rotate(0.5turn);\n\t\ttransform: rotate(100grad);\n\t\t/* Time units */\n\t\ttransition-duration: 300ms;\n\t\tanimation-duration: 2s;\n\t\t/* Resolution units */\n\t\tresolution: 300dpi;\n\t\tresolution: 2dppx;\n\t\tresolution: 96dpcm;\n\t}\n",
			"comment": null
		}
